{"tid":2064181,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"突破機構：九成人「不割席」願為香港付出","createTime":"2020-06-14T15:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T01:13:25.000Z","uid":20933,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"49f6b9e3f164d9f91ca12ea38a0325ab768d2d08","tid":2064181,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:19:44.000Z","msg":"突破去年10至11月以街頭訪問形式，訪問542名10至29歲的年輕人。調查結果發現，近75%受訪者感難過，抑鬱度以5分最高，受訪者的抑鬱度達2.8分。反修例運動的危機度評分以10為最高，評分達6.9分，逾72%認為危機源自「民主、人權、自由受削弱」，另有逾58%則認為是社會有不公義情況。逾90%受訪者亦表示在運動中經歷互相支持、打氣、在需要時會有人陪伴等情況。有91%人表明「不割席」，同意明白只要目標一致，就算表達或做法不同，大家都是「同路人」。<br />\n<br />\n研究亦發現，年輕人普遍對「香港人」身份有認同感，近96%認為自己與其他在香港生活的同是香港人，逾94%認為自己「越來越愛香港，願意為這裡的人付出」。機構指，年輕人對香港有承擔，視其他處身香港的人為一體。"},{"pid":"6e6d1e69803698e3fd7d31a140dd33aa49a78294","tid":2064181,"uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:19:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200614/BMSNW4TV37YGDLRT2FKUYOOACU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200614%2FBMSNW4TV37YGDLRT2FKUYOOACU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8gu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=32f0b0f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200614%2FBMSNW4TV37YGDLRT2FKUYOOACU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=b841a30a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200614/BMSNW4TV37YGDLRT2FKUYOOACU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"1fc0be284919915ca36d06e0af634192852d0f05","tid":2064181,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:21